Maintainer: Local Builder <builder@localhost>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), curl
Homepage: https://github.com/github/copilot-cli

Package: copilot
Architecture: amd64
Description: GitHub Copilot in the CLI.
 GitHub Copilot in the CLI provides a chat-like interface in the
 terminal that allows you to ask questions about the command line,
 generate shell commands, and explain commands.
